Welcome to Atlantis Country Club!
Centrally located in Palm Beach County, Florida, this club offers the elegance and comfort of a private resort in a picturesque, warm and friendly environment open to the public year-round. Offering championship golf to our members and the public, Atlantis Country Club has something for just about everyone.
